com.alexgilleran.icesoap.request

Interface SOAP11ListRequest<ResultType>

  • Type Parameters:
    ResultType - The type of the object to retrieve from this request. If the type is a List, you may want to consider using ListRequest instead.
    All Superinterfaces:
    ListRequest<ResultType,SOAP11Fault>, Request<List<ResultType>,SOAP11Fault>, SOAP11Request<List<ResultType>>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SOAP11ListRequestImpl

    public interface SOAP11ListRequest<ResultType>
extends ListRequest<ResultType,SOAP11Fault>, SOAP11Request<List<ResultType>>
    Extension of ListRequest that specifies a standard SOAP11Fault rather than specifying a specific one. This is the same interface as the v1.0.0 ListRequest.
    Author:
    Alex Gilleran
